race.comment: STROLL FUN (7) hit the ground running and set it up early clocking 22.40 with a 7 length win at this track over 400m. Winner at his latest appearance in the quickest time on the card. Well placed and can measure up. CATCH THE FEELS (1) was well off top last time, finishing 4th (25.93) in a OPEN at Q Lakeside. Has never missed the frame here at the trip including one win. The form from her last run stacks up well. Shapes as one to consider. FEARLESS PARKER (2) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, breaking through last time at Cannington over 381m. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Must be included in calculations. RUSTY ROCKET (5) was unplaced here last start but gets his chance to atone.
